        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/752/491/original/e6439ffd-98c4-485d-ba18-67fb81540ed8.png" srcset="" alt="Open Collaborations" height="232" width="172">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_46143ED0-1EE1-0135-7262-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Collaborations</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="start_a_new_collaboration" data-step-uuid="5C6B6F35-87FA-42D5-B743-3F70AD03B5F7">
